OL,3,CSchools closed due to snow and ice
OL,5,FDozens of schools are closed this
OL,6,Fmorning after much of Wales was hit by
OL,7,Fsnow and ice overnight.
OL,9,FPupils have been told to stay home in
OL,10,FDenbighshire, Conwy, Flintshire, Powys
OL,11,Fand Gwynedd
OL,13,FTransport for Wales said some rail
OL,14,Flines in the country are closed
OL,15,Fbecause of track damage following a
OL,16,Fperiod of "heavy wind, rain and snow".
OL,18,FBuses are replacing trains between
OL,19,FLlandudno Junction and Blaenau
OL,20,FFfestiniog until at least Monday.
