OL,3,CSchools closed due to snow and ice
OL,5,FA yellow warning for snow and ice
OL,6,Faffecting much of Wales has been
OL,7,Fissued until 11am. And a yellow ice
OL,8,Fwarning has been issued for south-east
OL,9,FWales until 10.30am.
OL,11,FA further warning has been issued for
OL,12,Fmuch of Wales across Thursday evening
OL,13,Finto Friday morning.
OL,15,FAs icy conditions persist, motorists
OL,16,Fare being urged to stick to major
OL,17,Froads that are most likely to have
OL,18,Fbeen gritted.
