OL,3,CSchools closed due to snow and ice
OL,5,FCar insurer RAC said it has seen the
OL,6,Fhighest levels of demand across the UK
OL,7,Ffor rescues in a three-day period
OL,8,Fsince December 2022.
OL,10,F"Cold conditions will last until at
OL,11,Fleast the weekend, so we urge drivers
OL,12,Fto remain vigilant of the risks posed
OL,13,Fby ice and, in some locations, snow,"
OL,14,Fsaid RAC breakdown spokeswoman Alice
OL,15,FSimpson. "Black ice on rural roads can
OL,16,Fbe impossible to spot, leaving very
OL,17,Flittle time to react if driving at
OL,18,Fspeed. Sticking to major roads that
OL,19,Fare most likely to have been gritted
OL,20,Fis strongly recommended."
